{"tid":274842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶) 阿朗串爆肥賓","createTime":"2017-06-07T15:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T15:27:50.000Z","uid":83128,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e056dc26f3c45d738dafe3b2ca36cd82bd307e64","tid":274842,"uid":83128,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"根據西班牙報章《El Pa&iacute;s》報道，肥賓成為皇馬主帥之初，曾委託助教整合大量進攻短片及圖片，存放到usb後把該usb交予C朗，期望後者好好研究後可以取得進步，在進攻端更具殺傷力。豈料葡萄牙球王原來也擁有一顆玻璃心，非但拒絕接受肥賓的usb見面禮，更回覆道：「<span style=\"color: red;\">告訴賓尼迪斯，我會把我的所有入球存放到一隻usb，之後把usb送給他慢慢研究。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n阿朗呢下又幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb847a42ea9f12352a612e93ba6ccbf6c08ecc3","tid":274842,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"牙朗踢波洗撚你教"},{"pid":"dc9d729b0d15fb605c4ef2f9ff070b8503efb59d","tid":274842,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"個新聞成年幾兩年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0378ec253b772cb53f11e15541da28d95c7c0690","tid":274842,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個新聞成年幾兩年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎番出黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812240241fc043ba8144bfbbf5de660159f4f0eb","tid":274842,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"