ba273c7e155eb253baf27c1a634d8d023bb","tid":274842,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"C&middot;朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）因為訓練賽中一個入球被吹罰無效，而當場發飆，對球隊主帥賓尼迪斯（Rafael Benitez）咆哮怒罵「Vai caralho！」（葡萄牙語，男性生殖器官），這位葡萄牙國腳以爆粗方式宣洩心中不滿，隨後又多次重複這個詞彙，但賓尼迪斯似乎並不為此困擾，只是微笑注視著球場。然而，C&middot;朗拿度的不滿還在繼續。隨後賓尼迪斯安排球員玩射門遊戲，輪流射橫楣，以提升射門精準度，但C朗卻憤怒地表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">皮球應該射入網內，而不是射橫楣！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n呢個都好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb3b39d784989c0092b6ea6e95ff2a207da44d7","tid":274842,"uid":187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢估係痢記啲前鋒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似獌狗隻連加特咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f5ea4c6245d29e5ec55dd3f707e68af0930561","tid":274842,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢估係痢記啲前鋒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似獌狗隻連加特咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥賓之前有無教過曼呀<br />\nOn9仔<br />\n死番去轉會post射精啦"},{"pid":"42b0a5e8c88ef48025d3f15c742a236f1659a6a3","tid":274842,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢估係痢記啲前鋒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似獌狗隻連加特咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\