學的研究項目，要求C.朗拿度參與其中，從射門時身體的姿勢，吃球的部位等方面進行改進，但是C.朗拿度卻對此感到反感。施丹的做法就非常聰明，他沒有要求C.朗拿度改進射門方式，反而和C.朗拿度一起進行自由球射門比賽，隨後親自傳授C.朗拿度主射自由球的技巧。<br />\n<br />\n高下立見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n老實講呢招有幾多教練用得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先你要係施丹"},{"pid":"1ad771525b9e254f1d5723f7bea70cc926c1c494","tid":274842,"uid":66433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:03:28.000Z","msg":"呢個球壇入面c朗應該淨係甘心聽費sir 拖舟 史高斯既指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e68892b90c740994dac71891a79beac453ed917","tid":274842,"uid":112232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:13:36.000Z","msg":"Cristaino Ronaldo<br />\n<br />\n&quot;When we were in training, I used to do a lot of tricks which hardly any players at the club could do. Once i was showing my skills to Scholes. After i finished it, Scholes took the ball and pointed to a tree which was about 50m from where we were standing. He said, I'm going to hit it in one shot. He kicked and hit the tree. He asked me to do the same; I kicked about 10 times, but still couldn't hit it, with that Accuracy. He smiled and left.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n排球仔型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62099942bd4f247ace12ed3a846a40cad69c51cd","tid":274842,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個球壇入面c朗應該淨係甘心聽費sir 拖舟 史高斯既指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個佢第二個老豆，一個球皇，一個佢前輩，𠎀斯都有d機既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25804738003c8a9735d66c1e856f586d1526b8ae","tid":274842,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cristaino Ronaldo<br />\n<br />\n&quot;When we were in training, I used to do a lot of tricks which hardly any players at the club could do. Once i was showing my skills to Scholes. After i finished it, Scholes took the ball and pointed to a tree which was about 50m from where we were standing. He said, I'm going to hit it in one shot. He kicked and hit the tree. He asked me to do the same; I kicked about 10 times, but still couldn't hit it, with that Accuracy. He smiled and left.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n排球仔型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不帶走一片雲彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725aff6aeb8a0b6acb4c451b0ec6bf5184437a44","tid":274842,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:30:15.000Z","msg":"去到C朗級咪又得拖丹教佢會服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b414dd41396b0d201fe26bd1e537237e0d2b45f","tid":274842,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"on撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個世界最頂級球員,仲要你咩睇人地片黎睇高自己<br />\n個陣佢都30歲啦<br />\n教練唔係咁做,你都係排兵佈陣練整體戰術之類<br />\n教牙朗踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果然只有施單可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3abe013e2154a7162c49fda45a3b8dac9b60207","tid":274842,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"C朗而家自由球咁撚廢&hellip;Bale同佢自由球比賽都贏鳩硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38906cf6d702a203fc3ea52b53168f6d4beb108d","tid":274842,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係幾撚寸，肥賓一片好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/